            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>


    <advantage name="Nuclear physics" type="technique">
        <cost points="4"/>
        <skill name="Physics"/>
        <short>The study of nuclear physics.</short>
        <description xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml">
            <para>
                You have a detailed knowledge of nuclear physics, and
                have a good understanding of how fusion and fission
                reactions occur and how atoms behave.
            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>

    <advantage name="Quantum physics" type="technique">
        <cost points="4"/>
        <skill name="Physics"/>
        <short>The study of quantum physics.</short>
        <description xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml">
            <para>
                You have a detailed knowledge of quantum physics,
                including the behaviour of particles at the quantum
                scales and the very basics of quantum gravity. If
                you also have <e>Computer hacking</e> you probably
                understand quantum computers, and knowledge of
                <e>Cryptography</e> will enable you to understand
                quantum encryption.
            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>

    <advantage name="Quantum gravity" type="technique">
        <cost points="6"/>
        <skill name="Physics"/>
        <prerequisite>Quantum physics</prerequisite>
        <short>The study of quantum gravity.</short>
        <description xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml">
            <para>
                You have a detailed knowledge of quantum gravity, how
                it describes the universe, and a good theoretical
                understanding of how grav technology really works.
            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>

    <advantage name="Relativity" type="technique">
        <cost points="4"/>
        <skill name="Physics"/>
        <short>The study of relativity.</short>
        <description xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml">
            <para>
                You have a detailed knowledge of relativity.
            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>

    <advantage name="Jump physics" type="technique">
        <cost points="6"/>
        <skill name="Physics"/>
        <prerequisite>Relativity</prerequisite>
        <short>The study of jump space.</short>
        <description xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml">
            <para>
                You have a detailed knowledge of jump space, and know
                how (at the theoretical level) jump drives work.
            </para>
        </description>
    </advantage>

